OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fwith further outbreaks of mostly light
OL,7,Fand patchy rain and drizzle initially.
OL,8,FStrengthening winds will herald a band
OL,9,Fof heavier rain later in the night,
OL,10,Fpushing eastwards through the early
OL,11,Fhours. Risk of coastal gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,14,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fblustery showers following. These
OL,16,Flocally heavy with hail and a risk of
OL,17,Fthunder during the afternoon. Windier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
